 priority filtering
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Notifications are events, not measurements — every source's notification
must be delivered. The priority filter ran before the notification API
extracted notifications.* paths from the delta, so a low-ranked source's
alarm could be silently dropped if a higher-ranked source had recently
sent any value for the same notification path.

Short-circuit notifications.* paths in the toPreferredDelta reducer so
they bypass priority filtering entirely. Mirror the rule in the admin UI
by hiding notification paths from the unconfigured-multi-source warning
and the path-override picker.
